                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.00/18417</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Special Representative <persName type="from"
                            >Rodgers</persName> to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Extract]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Mexico City</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1916-06-13T12:00:00-06:36">
                            <hi rend="italic">June 13, 1916, noon</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>142. In reply to Department’s 131, June 12, 5 p.m. Brought matter attention
                    authorities last night. This morning informed by Foreign Office information just
                    received de la Rosa prisoner with Mexican authorities Matamoros.</p>
                <pb facs="0651" n="575" xml:id="pg_575"/>
                <p>In relation to de la Rosa had filed previously four urgent written
                    representations and have discussed his actions at Foreign Office at least six
                    times, result always being promises investigation and no announced result except
                    general allegation nothing wrong.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Rodgers</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
